{"tid":629971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科大印度生入侵電郵　扮教授要求同事出「指定試題」","createTime":"2018-04-15T07:19:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T03:22:10.000Z","uid":73179,"like":180,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"c934a92f343b93615511a4c291a617a61f7d4567","tid":629971,"uid":73179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:19:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180415/bkn-20180415030203597-0415_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180415%2Fbkn-20180415030203597-0415_00822_001.html&d=f8iRq13rN6MEZzm0wnae03Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6711a9aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180415/bkn-20180415030203597-0415_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"42823da6cad5f6b64f7cc924adf0da1d5c3aaf0c","tid":629971,"uid":162268,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"c934a92f343b93615511a4c291a617a61f7d4567","tid":629971,"uid":73179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T07:19:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180415/bkn-20180415030203597-0415_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180415%2Fbkn-20180415030203597-0415_00822_001.html&d=f8iRq13rN6MEZzm0wnae03Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=6711a9aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180415/bkn-20180415030203597-0415_00822_001.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T08:00:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 棟樑"},{"pid":"17c7a72016ff522aa34e108113d381528a65b46f","tid":629971,"uid":22675,"like":187,"dislike":0,"score":187,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T08:01:47.000Z","msg":"印度男生涉入侵教授電郵被捕。消息指，本月初一名攻讀科學的印度男學生（21歲），在學科考試前一日，疑入侵一名姓劉（41歲）男教授的學校電郵，並利用其名義傳電郵給另一名負責出卷的教授，要求該教授出指定的考試題目。但由於考試卷早已印好，故出卷教授未有理會，考試題目亦未有受到影響。 <br />\n<br />\n據了解，2名涉事的教授當事並沒有為意，直至上周四（12日），2名教授閒談時聊到此事，始揭發事件，2人立即通知學校的資訊科技部，經初步檢查後，懷疑劉的電子郵箱被人入侵，商議後決定報警。警方初步調查後，於昨日（14日），在香港仔一單位拘捕涉案男生，涉嫌「不誠實使用電腦」，案件交將軍澳警區刑事調查隊跟進。 <br />\n<br />\n據悉，涉案印度男生並非交流生，事後有人指自己雖然主修科學，但素來對電腦科有著濃厚興趣，是次犯案只是一時貪玩，想一展身手，事後感到十分後悔。 <br />\n<br />\n香港科技大學發言人指，校方於上週四（ 12日）向警方舉報一宗懷疑電腦入侵事件，由於案件已交警方調查，大學不便作進一步評論。校方會盡力協助警方調查。科大現已採用雙重認證技術加強網絡保安功能，今次入侵屬個別事件，大學會定期檢視及提升網絡安全系統。"},{"pid":"d1e42ba00d6e5a38ed06355b8c504613d66b55a6","tid":629971,"uid":73179,"like":31,"dislike":3,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T08:05:57.000Z","msg":"Thank you 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 電話copy唔到"},{"pid":"4999935fbe0a3203a681c2f7084a4a879aac7730","tid":629971,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T08:09:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d53f5470b9371ff7fc97dddbf0b97254bcf05fee","tid":629971,"uid":42407,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T08:10:51.000Z","msg":"救教學"},{"pid":"236a070fc17268cbd31e024ca0452d182432a45e","tid":629971,"uid":99816,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T08:11:25.000Z","msg":"on9仔"},{"pid":"b427351f58eb47c4eaf4da2f2c94e2d6d43a407a","tid":629971,"uid":99816,"like":91,"dislike":1,"score":90,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T08:11:42.000Z","msg":"UST得一分"},{"pid":"9b0f4feefa13b538eb83cec11b0ae6f27f510b87","tid":629971,"uid":41508,"like":174,"dislike":9,"score":165,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T08:12:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c7618731540a77cc1dae247ca2b77bbd8926ef21","tid":629971,"uid":47359,"like":279,"dislike":4,"score":275,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T08:13:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">@ust南亞狗</span>"},{"pid":"30cf03a2f58884884e1d6cb265b34498ec78e674","tid":629971,"uid":52480,"like":